title: Mirror of Germany. No. 173 = Deutschland Spiegel
brief_description:
Episode of Series “Mirror of Germany. The German Scene = Deutschland Spiegel”.
Magazine items: The International Riding and Show Jumping Contest in Berlin and agricultural show; Harold Wilson in Berlin; a new museum dedicated to German expressionist artists; Dortmund in the Rhine-Ruhr area; Wuppertal’s monorail suspension railway and famous Clock Museum; the European figure skating and ice dancing championships; skiing and the first synthetic ice toboggan track.
